1.1.name: wordpress/showcase-idx
1.1.description: Showcase IDX for WordPress is a state-of-the-art, map-centric real estate search platform. You must first be a member of an MLS and must have access to IDX data in order to use our service. Additionally, a subscription to Showcase IDX is required. Please visit showcaseidx.com to setup your account. Once you have an API key, simply enter it into the top-level "Showcase IDX" admin menu.
